    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it will soon require new brake pads and a suspension tune-up to address some minor rattling over bumps. It is a functional, honest car that reflects its age and mileage, perfect for a buyer looking for a budget-friendly option.",
      "price": 19500.0,
