    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle exhibits a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. The exterior retains its original showroom luster, complemented by an interior that remains in pristine, untouched condition. Every component has been rigorously vetted to ensure uncompromising performance and reliability.",
      "price": 45900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2003 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance is complete: rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system has been overhauled with uprated seals, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced. The suspension remains tight with original M-spec geometry, and the underbody is free of oxidation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Low mileage. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standard. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like gloss with zero stone chips or swirl marks, all protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of compression or wear, and the interior still carries its original factory aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history and a recent multi-point inspection confirming that every system operates exactly as intended. It has been exclusively garage-kept under a soft cover and never exposed to inclement weather. This sale includes both original keys, all owner's manuals, and the original window sticker. This is an investment-grade example tailored for the most discerning collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest possible standards. This vehicle remains in showroom-grade condition, exhibiting no discernible wear on the hand-finished interior or the original factory paint. Meticulously preserved and mechanically flawless, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. We invite you to experience this uncompromising example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so excited to show you this car. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such pristine condition that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been garage-kept, pampered, and it\u2019s sparkling clean inside and out\u2014seriously, not a speck of dust. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for some fun adventures, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for this beauty to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a peek!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade performance icon in concours-ready condition. This specimen features a high-revving, naturally aspirated power plant with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated variable valve timing system, delivering linear power across the entire tachometer. The drivetrain is anchored by a close-ratio six-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring surgical precision through the corners. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, supported by a pristine multi-link suspension and original forged alloy wheels. Every mechanical component, from the cooling system's expansion tank to the subframe bushings, remains in peak operational state. The exterior maintains its original factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the interior preserves its original tactile integrity. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the automotive purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
